Important
	* Build-in debugging (extended logging)
	* More meaningful SMTP error messages when remote server fails

Normal
	* Improve glue parser (especially for fetchmail)
	* Local domain/MDA support
	* Kerberos auth

Considerations
	* Support for netrc configuration files
	* Filtering
	* Stand-alone architecture with auth module (root user),
	  config module (local user) and SMTP module (nobody user)
